            "ratingValue": "3",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The management of exam dates is very bad, I experienced from last 3 to 4 years that they schedule exams near national holidays and festivals so one can`t plan vacations. For example they held exams from 18 Dec to 29 Dec now most people plan vacations due to last month but in this case how can we plan. Similarly they held exams near Holi & diwali.",
          "publisher": {
