            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Homerton Grammar School - Sector 21A"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "shweta narang"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-08-16",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We extend our heartfelt thanks to Homerton Grammar School for organizing a wonderful celebration, especially for the Father's celebration coffee morning event. The students of Class 1 and 2 truly outdid themselves, putting in tremendous effort to deliver flawless performances that delighted everyone present. The car racing activity was a fantastic addition, bringing joy and excitement to the day.\n\nWe are also thrilled to witness the launch of the AI and Robotics program. It's incredibly encouraging to see young minds being introduced to such essential skills, preparing them for the workforce of the future. This initiative is a great step forward in ensuring that our children are well-equipped for the challenges ahead.\n\nThank you to all the teachers, students and members of the management team.\n\nIn addition to this we would like to express our deepest gratitude to Priyanka Mam  for her unwavering dedication and support to\nEzra Narang - Class 1 S .Your guidance, patience, and encouragement have made a significant impact on Ezra's learning journey.\nThank you for being such a wonderful teacher and for creating a positive and enriching environment in your classroom.\n\nWith sincere appreciation,\n\n[Shweta and Divij Narang]",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
