            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "it was really a good function, All children given  awesome performance and we all enjoyed  a lot on that day specially children's performance on Sapna story, gymnastic and robot dance . It shows the hardwork of teachers and management who created such a powerful event. We wish it Will be continue in the future with more power .\nCongratulations to all staff and management for doing such a wonderful event in school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
