            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Dear Mam!\n\nI wanted to take a moment to express my heartfelt appreciation for the wonderful Father's Day event organized by the school. It was a truly special day that allowed me to spend quality time with my child and create lasting memories.\n\nThe activities/programmes were engaging, entertaining, and well-organized. I loved seeing the performance of tots!🥰\n\nThe event was a great way to recognize and celebrate the importance of fathers....\n\nThank you to the teachers, managerial staff and volunteers who worked tirelessly to make this event a success.\n\nLooking forward to more events like this in the future!\n\nBest regards,\nBhawna\nMother of Vrinda and Anant",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
